@database UrltextClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Urltext Class"


Urltext class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Urltext class is used to show a simple text object that is
  highlighted when the mouse is over it and that opens an url via
  OpenURL if clicked.

  Note that Urltext.mcc is a subclass of Area.mui and not of
  Text.mui; it means that the value of Text attribute must be
  pure ascii rather than MUI text. Urltext is a subclass of
  Urltext.mcc so you must have Urltext.mcc in MUI:Libs/MUI to use
  it.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Active@{fg text}
  B G
  It's 1 if openurl.library was found and so the object may be
  clicked, 0 otherwise

  @{fg shine}DoOpenURL@{fg text}
  B I
  If set to 1 (default), the url is reached when the user clicks
  the object.
  If set to 0, nothing happens when the user clicks the object.

  @{fg shine}DoVisitedPen@{fg text}
  B I
  When the object is clicked with success, which means OpenURL
  was able to find a client for that url, the text is rendered in
  MUI Mark color. Default 0

  @{fg shine}FallBack@{fg text}
  B ISGN
  If openurl.library is not installed in the system and FallBack
  is 1, the object is still active (but of course clicking on it
  does procure no action), if FallBack is 0 the object is
  rendered with MUI Text pen. Default 1

  @{fg shine}NoMenu@{fg text}
  B I
  If set to 1,you get no context menu.

  @{fg shine}SetMax@{fg text}
  I I
  If set to 1 (default), the object is x-limited.
  If set to 0, the object is x-unlimited.

  @{fg shine}Text@{fg text}
  S IG
  The text to show. If not supplied or empty, Url is used

  @{fg shine}Underline@{fg text}
  B ISGN
  Underline the text. Default 1

  @{fg shine}Url@{fg text}
  S IGN IND
  The url to open. Note that it must be supplied and that its is
  notified everytime the mouse is over the object

  @{fg shine}Visited@{fg text}
  B GN
  Set to 1 and notified, when the user clicks the object for the
  first time.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  @{fg shine}OpenURL@{fg text}
  -
  Opens the url as the object has been clicked.

@EndNode

